{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Combine","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Combine\/Publishers"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A publisher that emits a scheduler’s current time on a repeating interval."}],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"ComposableArchitecture","relatedModules":["Combine"]}],"externalID":"s:7Combine10PublishersO0A10SchedulersE5TimerC","symbolKind":"class","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"Timer"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"Timer"}],"title":"Publishers.Timer","roleHeading":"Class","extendedModule":"Combine","platforms":[{"unavailable":false,"introducedAt":"13.0","beta":false,"deprecated":false,"name":"iOS"},{"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"10.15","unavailable":false,"beta":false,"name":"macOS"},{"beta":false,"introducedAt":"13.0","name":"tvOS","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false},{"beta":false,"name":"watchOS","introducedAt":"6.0","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false}]},"relationshipsSections":[{"type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/7Combine20ConnectablePublisherP","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/7Combine9PublisherP"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"final"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"Timer"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"text":"Scheduler","kind":"genericParameter"},{"text":"> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"where","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Scheduler"},{"text":" : ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Scheduler","preciseIdentifier":"s:7Combine9SchedulerP"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"overview","text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This publisher is an alternative to Foundation’s "},{"code":"Timer.publisher","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", with its primary"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"difference being that it allows you to use any scheduler for the timer, not just "},{"code":"RunLoop","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"This is useful because the "},{"code":"RunLoop","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" scheduler is not testable in the sense that if you want","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"to write tests against a publisher that makes use of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Timer.publisher"},{"text":" you must explicitly","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"wait for time to pass in order to get emissions. This is likely to lead to fragile tests and"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"greatly bloat the time your tests take to execute."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"It can be used much like Foundation’s timer, except you specify a scheduler rather than a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"run loop:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["Publishers.Timer(every: .seconds(1), scheduler: DispatchQueue.main)","  .autoconnect()","  .sink { print(\"Timer\", $0) }"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"But more importantly, you can use it with "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"TestScheduler"},{"type":"text","text":" so that any Combine code you write"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"involving timers becomes more testable. This shows how we can easily simulate the idea of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"moving time forward 1,000 seconds in a timer:","type":"text"}]},{"code":["let scheduler = DispatchQueue.test","var output: [Int] = []","","Publishers.Timer(every: 1, scheduler: scheduler)","  .autoconnect()","  .sink { _ in output.append(output.count) }","  .store(in: &self.cancellables)","","XCTAssertEqual(output, [])","","scheduler.advance(by: 1)","XCTAssertEqual(output, [0])","","scheduler.advance(by: 1)","XCTAssertEqual(output, [0, 1])","","scheduler.advance(by: 1_000)","XCTAssertEqual(output, Array(0...1_001))"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"}],"kind":"content"}],"topicSections":[{"title":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Combine\/Publishers\/Timer\/init(every:tolerance:scheduler:options:)"]},{"title":"Instance Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Combine\/Publishers\/Timer\/interval","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Combine\/Publishers\/Timer\/options","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Combine\/Publishers\/Timer\/scheduler","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Combine\/Publishers\/Timer\/tolerance"]},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Combine\/Publishers\/Timer\/connect()","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Combine\/Publishers\/Timer\/receive(subscriber:)"],"title":"Instance Methods"},{"title":"Type Aliases","identifiers":["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Combine\/Publishers\/Timer\/Failure","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Combine\/Publishers\/Timer\/Output"]},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Combine\/Publishers\/Timer\/ConnectablePublisher-Implementations","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentat